		{
			"x": 5789.861865152914,
			"y": 2158.5652471544636,
			"rotation": 0,
			"isLocked": false,
			"opacity": 1,
			"meta": {},
			"id": "shape:1aCn4oBlzni4AuxGTyCM7",
			"type": "text",
			"props": {
				"color": "black",
				"size": "xl",
				"w": 1255.4453125,
				"text": "Difference between Virual Private Server & Physical Server:",
				"font": "serif",
				"textAlign": "start",
				"autoSize": true,
				"scale": 1
			},
			"parentId": "page:page",
			"index": "aQ4m9",
			"typeName": "shape"
		},
		{
			"x": 5785.380479261227,
			"y": 2259.2204264042107,
			"rotation": 0,
			"isLocked": false,
			"opacity": 1,
			"meta": {},
			"id": "shape:2Oe99TNt0pfV5feOxsOdr",
			"type": "text",
			"props": {
				"color": "black",
				"size": "xl",
				"w": 2359.0546875,
				"text": "| Feature                       | VPS (Virtual Private Server)                                                 | Physical Server                                           \n| ---------------------- | --------------------------------------------------------------| ---------------------------------------         \n| **Nature**                | Virtual machine running on shared hardware           | Actual physical computer                        \n| **Resources**         | Assigned portion of CPU, RAM, disk                                | Full CPU, RAM, disk                                    \n| **Cost**                     | Cheaper, pay for what you use                                            | Expensive, full machine cost                  \n| **Isolation**            | Isolated from other VPS on the same host                     | Fully isolated (nothing else shares it) \n| **Scalability**        | Easy to resize resources (add RAM/CPU/disk)              | Harder, requires new hardware           \n| **Management**   | Managed through control panel or SSH                          | Fully manual, you maintain hardware|\n| **Setup speed**     | Instant (minutes)                                                                      | Takes time (buy/setup/shipping)         \n---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------",
				"font": "serif",
				"textAlign": "start",
				"autoSize": true,
				"scale": 1
			},
			"parentId": "page:page",
			"index": "aR2Pn",
			"typeName": "shape"
		},
