				"color": "black",
				"size": "xl",
				"w": 2616.671875,
				"text": "What is a Data Center?\n\nPhysical location where thousands (or millions) of servers are stored and managed.\nThink of it like a warehouse of computers, connected with high-speed internet, power backup, cooling systems, and security.\nCloud providers put their servers in these data centers and then virtualize them so you can rent a piece (a VPS) remotely.",
